ZH: 我睡在床上。
EN: I sleep on the bed.

ZH: 这床很舒服。
EN: This bed is very comfortable.

ZH: 我在床上看电视。
EN: I watch TV in bed.

ZH: 床很大，可以睡两个人。
EN: The bed is big enough for two people to sleep.

ZH: 我每天晚上都在床上读书。
EN: I read books in bed every night.

ZH: 床上有一条蓝色的毛毯。
EN: There is a blue blanket on the bed.

ZH: 不要在床上吃东西。
EN: Don't eat on the bed.

ZH: 请把床整理好。
EN: Please make the bed.

ZH: 妈妈昨天买了一张新床。
EN: Mom bought a new bed yesterday.

ZH: 我喜欢清晨一起床就看到阳光。
EN: I like waking up to the sunlight in the morning.

ZH: 床边有一个小桌子，上面放着一本书。
EN: There is a small table next to the bed, with a book on it.

ZH: 床头有个灯，可以随时打开或关闭。
EN: There is a lamp by the bed that can be turned on or off at any time.

ZH: 我想买一张软软的床垫。
EN: I want to buy a soft mattress.

ZH: 我的猫喜欢躺在床上晒太阳。
EN: My cat likes to lie on the bed and bask in the sun.

ZH: 给我来一床干净的床单。
EN: Give me a clean bed sheet.

ZH: 我把书放在了床边的抽屉里。
EN: I put the book in the drawer next to the bed.

ZH: 她病得很重，一天都不能离开床。
EN: She is really sick and can't leave the bed all day.

ZH: 我的床上有一只坏掉的弹簧。
EN: There is a broken spring in my bed.

ZH: 玩具都散落在床上。
EN: Toys are scattered on the bed.

ZH: 她用细绳在床的四角系上了蚊帐。
EN: She tied the mosquito net to the four corners of the bed with a thin rope.
